OL,5,Ctweet
OL,7,FLucy Connolly, who was jailed for
OL,8,Finciting racial hatred in the
OL,9,Faftermath of the Southport terror
OL,10,Fattack, is reportedly set to be
OL,11,Freleased from prison.
OL,13,FConnolly, the wife of Conservative
OL,14,Fcouncillor Raymond Connolly, will be
OL,15,Freleased on Thursday after being
OL,16,Fsentenced last year to 31 months in
OL,17,Fcustody, the Telegraph reported.
