OL,3,CLucy Connolly set to be released from
OL,4,Cprison following jail term for hate
OL,5,Ctweet
OL,7,FShe had posted on X on the day of the
OL,8,Fmurder of three children by Axel
OL,9,FRudakubana in Southport: "Mass
OL,10,Fdeportation now, set fire to all the
OL,11,Ff****** hotels full of the bastards
OL,12,Ffor all I care... if that makes me
OL,13,Fracist so be it."
OL,15,FShe pleaded guilty to inciting racial
OL,16,Fhatred by publishing and distributing
OL,17,F"threatening or abusive" written
OL,18,Fmaterial on X and was jailed at
OL,19,FBirmingham Crown Court in October last
OL,20,Fyear.
