OL,7,FAsked during Prime Minister's
OL,8,FQuestions whether her imprisonment was
OL,9,Fan "efficient or fair use" of prison,
OL,10,FSir Keir said: "Sentencing is a matter
OL,11,Ffor our courts, and I celebrate the
OL,12,Ffact that we have independent courts
OL,13,Fin this country.
OL,15,F"I am strongly in favour of free
OL,16,Fspeech, we've had free speech in this
OL,17,Fcountry for a very long time and we
OL,18,Fprotect it fiercely.
