OL,7,F"But I am equally against incitement
OL,8,Fto violence against other people. I
OL,9,Fwill always support the action taken
OL,10,Fby our police and courts to keep our
OL,11,Fstreets and people safe."
OL,13,FConnolly's post was viewed 310,000
OL,14,Ftimes in three-and-a-half hours before
OL,15,Fshe deleted it.
