OL,5,Ctweet
OL,7,FLord Young of Acton, founder and
OL,8,Fdirector of the Free Speech Union,
OL,9,Fsaid: "The fact that Lucy Connolly has
OL,10,Fspent more than a year in prison for a
OL,11,Fsingle tweet that she quickly deleted
OL,12,Fand apologised for is a national
OL,13,Fscandal, particularly when Labour MPs,
OL,14,Fcouncillors and anti-racism
OL,15,Fcampaigners who've said and done much
OL,16,Fworse have avoided jail.
OL,18,F"The same latitude they enjoyed should
OL,19,Fhave been granted to Lucy."
